45
00:03:21,860 --> 00:03:23,362
<i>She's worth a hundred employees.</i>

46
00:03:23,445 --> 00:03:26,156
<i>If her boss is really watching,
he should give her a bonus.</i>

47
00:03:26,782 --> 00:03:30,369
