so it can't be helped, but…

238
00:15:55,530 --> 00:16:00,034
Fine. I'll buy you
a more expensive meal next time.

239
00:16:00,118 --> 00:16:01,619
I'll be looking forward to it.

240
00:16:02,287 --> 00:16:03,621
