242
00:16:05,832 --> 00:16:06,791
<i>Omakase</i>?

243
00:16:09,002 --> 00:16:09,919
Careful.

244
00:16:10,420 --> 00:16:11,921
No peeking.

245
00:16:12,005 --> 00:16:13,047
Okay.

246
00:16:13,131 --> 00:16:14,674
